data.description: Beautiful Hyde Park duplex!  Have your upstairs tenants pay your mortgage or rent out the main level of this generously sized 1600 sqft, 3-bed units. Each unit has laundry in the kitchen, quartz counters, hardwood & laminate wood floors. Historical charm with modern convenience updates can be viewed throughout. Each unit has updated electrical, plumbing, and HVAC. Unfinished basement ideal for storage, enough for both units. Buyers agent to confirm room measurements, lot size, square footage and school district information.
